Nahed Yousri (Arabic: ناهد يسري), nke a na-akpọkwa Nahied Yousri, (amụrụ na 10 Mee 1949) bụ onye Ijipt na-eme ihe nkiri.
A mụrụ ya Nahed Hassan Shukri, ọ sooro nwanne ya nwanyị Samia Shukri ma mee ihe nkiri mbụ ya na 1965

N'ịgbaso ọrụ na-abawanye, ọrụ ya dị egwu bịara na The Lady of the Black Moons (1971), na A Woman of Fire (1971) n'ihu Salah Zulfikar bụ nke gara nke ọma n'ahịa ma ọtụtụ ihe nkiri Lebanọn ndị ọzọ na-egosipụtakarị ya n'ọnọdụ ndị na-akpali agụụ mmekọahụ
N'etiti afọ 1980, ọ rụrụ ọrụ na usoro ihe nkiri TV dị iche iche nke Egypt
Ọ lara ezumike nká na ihe nkiri Yasin Ismail Yasin nke 1990 a kpọrọ Disappeared Wife.
